0.0.1.about: Python Brasil [13] is the annual conference hosted by PythonBrasil community. It will be bringing together developers, experts, researchers, scientists, enthusiasts and companies dealing in python. It is a completely volunteer driven event, managed by PythonBrasil(https://2017.pythonbrasil.org.br/) Python Delhi Users Group. On its maiden year Python Brasil [13] attracted a total attendance of 300 people.
